description: |
  Legal document analysis toolkit for automatic processing of court docket information.

  This toolkit enables private, local analysis of legal documents using Docker-based AI models,
  with a focus on timeline generation, sentiment analysis, and factual information extraction.
  All processing happens locally with no external API calls to maintain complete confidentiality.

  The system is designed to process various document formats (PDF, DOCX, TXT) and generate
  chronological timelines of events with objective sentiment analysis to identify potential
  inconsistencies or patterns in documentation.
